                terms carefully, and keep a copy of them for your reference.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Electronic Communications</h2>
            <p>
                Visiting line-properties.com or sending emails to Line
                Properties inc constitutes electronic communications. You
                consent to receive electronic communications and you agree that
                all agreements, notices, disclosures and other communications
