        <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Cancellation/Refund Policy</h2>
            <p>
                We issue a full refund for cancellations 30 days before
                check-in. We issue a full refund for cancellations within 48
                hours of booking only if the check-in date is at least 14 days
                away. We issue a 50% refund for cancellations at least 14 days
                before check-in. We do not issue refunds for cancellations made
                within 14 days of check-in.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Contact Us</h2>
            <address>
                Line Properties Inc<br />
